2025-09-12 13:44:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:25 [INFO] Can continue: Ilfeen
2025-09-12 13:44:25 [INFO] Can continue: So what happened?
2025-09-12 13:44:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:26 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:26 [INFO] Can continue: I entered the library and found the seal broken by<br>Lord Iorwerth.
