2025-09-12 13:44:28 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:28 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:28 [INFO] Can continue: Yes, it contained a memory, left behind by Seren<br>herself.
