2025-09-12 13:44:30 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:30 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:30 [INFO] Can continue: It was only part of something larger though. I had to<br>break the other eight seals to uncover the rest of it.
2025-09-12 13:44:30 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:31 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:31 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 13:44:31 [INFO] Can continue: So you managed to break all of Seren's seals? Very<br>impressive PLAYER_NAME. Now tell us, this memory, what was<br>it?
2025-09-12 13:44:31 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:32 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:32 [INFO] Can continue: That's where it gets interesting... The memory spoke of<br>a curse on the elves, a curse that Seren was<br>desperately trying to break.
2025-09-12 13:44:32 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:33 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 13:44:33 [INFO] Can continue: A curse? What curse?
2025-09-12 13:44:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:34 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:34 [INFO] Can continue: A curse binding the elves to Seren. As long as she<br>remained close, it was unnoticeable, but if she went too<br>far... pain, and death.
2025-09-12 13:44:34 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:36 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:44:36 [INFO] Can continue: But who was responsible? Who cursed our people?
2025-09-12 13:44:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:37 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:37 [INFO] Can continue: That's the thing... It was Seren herself.
2025-09-12 13:44:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:38 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 13:44:38 [INFO] Can continue: ...
2025-09-12 13:44:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:39 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 13:44:39 [INFO] Can continue: What?
2025-09-12 13:44:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:40 [INFO] LAG DETECTED 784ms
2025-09-12 13:44:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:40 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:44:40 [INFO] Can continue: Seren was our goddess, she would never curse us. How<br>dare you suggest otherwise!
