2025-09-12 13:44:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:45 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:45 [INFO] Can continue: She didn't mean to do it, she was trying to help. She<br>was using her own essence to try and extend your<br>lifespans, it just went wrong...
