2025-09-12 13:44:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:48 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:48 [INFO] Can continue: Seren went to great lengths to undo the curse. She<br>believed that she could nullify it by creating a being of<br>darkness, one to counter her light essence.
