2025-09-12 13:44:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:49 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 13:44:49 [INFO] Can continue: You don't mean...
2025-09-12 13:44:49 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:44:51 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:44:51 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:44:51 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth spoke the truth. She created a fragment<br>of herself, filled with darkness, hoping to use it to break<br>the curse. It didn't work though, so she sealed it in the<br>Temple of Light.
