2025-09-12 13:46:21 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:46:21 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:46:21 [INFO] Can continue: Here is the clue he left behind:<br>'The trees of my home will call to me.'
2025-09-12 13:46:21 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:46:22 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:46:22 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:46:22 [INFO] Can continue: I see, anything else I should know?
2025-09-12 13:46:22 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:46:23 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:46:23 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:46:23 [INFO] Can continue: The Crwys clan is a clan of woodcutters and farmers.<br>The entire clan is close to nature, but none more than<br>Lord Crwys.
