2025-09-12 13:46:31 [INFO] Can continue: The Hefin clan are our religious leaders. They teach us<br>to better ourselves, not just in mind, but in body as<br>well. Lady Hefin used to lead some of the more<br>vigorous training exercises of the Hefin clan.
