2025-09-12 13:54:02 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:02 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:02 [INFO] Can continue: Oh... Hello. Good work finding Lord Crwys and Lady<br>Hefin. I never thought I'd see the other elders again,<br>maybe we'll have a chance with them alongside us.
2025-09-12 13:54:02 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:03 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:03 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:54:03 [INFO] Can continue: No problem. Any news from Ysgawyn?
2025-09-12 13:54:03 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:04 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:04 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:04 [INFO] Can continue: He has just returned. Let us gather the others and<br>hear what he has to say.
2025-09-12 13:54:04 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:06 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:07 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian calls the others to the meeting.
2025-09-12 13:54:07 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:09 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:09 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:09 [INFO] Can continue: Now that Ysgawyn has returned, I thought we should<br>gather to hear what he has discovered.
2025-09-12 13:54:09 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:10 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 13:54:10 [INFO] Can continue: Where is Arianwyn?
2025-09-12 13:54:10 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:11 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:11 [INFO] Can continue: Elena
2025-09-12 13:54:11 [INFO] Can continue: I saw him heading out into the forest earlier. He must<br>have wanted some time alone.
2025-09-12 13:54:11 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:12 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:12 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 13:54:12 [INFO] Can continue: I hope he's okay.
2025-09-12 13:54:12 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Can continue: He'll be alright, just give him time. While he is gone, we<br>need to keep making progress.
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Can continue: On that note, what news do you have, Ysgawyn?
2025-09-12 13:54:13 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:15 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:15 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:15 [INFO] Can continue: The shrine at Gorlah was empty. The orb was removed<br>quite a while ago by the looks of things.
2025-09-12 13:54:15 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:16 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:16 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:54:16 [INFO] Can continue: So do you believe me now?
2025-09-12 13:54:16 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:17 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:17 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:17 [INFO] Can continue: If it helps with your overinflated ego, then yes, I now<br>believe you.
2025-09-12 13:54:17 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:18 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 13:54:18 [INFO] Can continue: If the orb isn't at Gorlah, Lord Iorwerth must have<br>claimed it. It could be anywhere now.
2025-09-12 13:54:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:19 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:19 [INFO] Can continue: Well luckily for us, I know exactly where it is. There's<br>a cave just north of the Iorwerth Camp that is used to<br>store supplies. Lord Iorwerth has it under close guard<br>there.
2025-09-12 13:54:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:20 [INFO] Can continue: Ilfeen
2025-09-12 13:54:20 [INFO] Can continue: How do you know this?
2025-09-12 13:54:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:21 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:21 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:21 [INFO] Can continue: Because I went scouting.
2025-09-12 13:54:21 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:22 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:22 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:22 [INFO] Can continue: Scouting? At the Iorwerth Camp? Who gave you<br>permission?
2025-09-12 13:54:22 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Can continue: I gave myself permission. I do not serve you,<br>Baxtorian, or anyone else here.
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Can continue: No, you just serve yourself, don't you Ysgawyn?
2025-09-12 13:54:24 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:25 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:25 [INFO] Can continue: My actions benefit us all! Now that we know where the<br>orb is, we can move to claim it.
2025-09-12 13:54:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:27 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 13:54:27 [INFO] Can continue: But why would Lord Iorwerth keep the orb at the<br>camp? Surely it would be more secure behind the<br>Prifddinas walls.
2025-09-12 13:54:27 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:28 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:28 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:28 [INFO] Can continue: That's the other thing I found out. Lord Iorwerth<br>knows we managed to enter the library. He fears the<br>orb would not be safe behind the walls.
2025-09-12 13:54:28 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:29 [INFO] [GAME] <col=8f4808>Your stamina enhancement is about to expire.</col>
2025-09-12 13:54:29 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:29 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:29 [INFO] Can continue: How did you discover this?
2025-09-12 13:54:29 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:30 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:30 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:30 [INFO] Can continue: I have my methods...
2025-09-12 13:54:30 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:31 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:31 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:31 [INFO] Can continue: It worries me that you are unwilling to share them.
2025-09-12 13:54:31 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:33 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:33 [INFO] Can continue: Save your suspicions for someone who cares.
2025-09-12 13:54:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:34 [INFO] Can continue: Ilfeen
2025-09-12 13:54:34 [INFO] Can continue: So we know where the orb is. What do we do now?
2025-09-12 13:54:34 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:36 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:36 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth intends to use the orb to free the dark<br>fragment of Seren. We need to stop him.
2025-09-12 13:54:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:37 [INFO] Can continue: Eluned
2025-09-12 13:54:37 [INFO] Can continue: But this fragment of Seren, it's still part of her. Lord<br>Iorwerth has done some unspeakable things, but he<br>doesn't serve Zamorak like we thought, maybe we can<br>reason with him.
2025-09-12 13:54:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:38 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:38 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:38 [INFO] Can continue: I tried to reason with Lord Iorwerth a long time ago...<br>It won't work, as much as I wish it would.
2025-09-12 13:54:38 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:39 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:39 [INFO] Can continue: Regardless of his intentions, Lord Iorwerth is our<br>enemy. You should want to kill him, not reason with<br>him.
2025-09-12 13:54:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:40 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:40 [INFO] Can continue: I would never wish for the death of a fellow elf, no<br>matter what they've done.
2025-09-12 13:54:40 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:41 [INFO] [GAME] <col=8f4808>Your stamina enhancement has expired.</col>
2025-09-12 13:54:41 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:41 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:41 [INFO] Can continue: Well look at you with your moral high ground.
2025-09-12 13:54:41 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:43 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:43 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:43 [INFO] Can continue: Now is not the time for arguing. At some point, we will<br>need to decide what to do about the fragment of Seren.<br>For now though, we need to focus on getting that orb<br>and stopping Lord Iorwerth.
2025-09-12 13:54:43 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:45 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:45 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 13:54:45 [INFO] Can continue: The orb isn't enough for him to win though, he'll also<br>need to break through the defences on the Temple of<br>Light. He'll struggle to do that now he's lost Ardougne.
2025-09-12 13:54:45 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:46 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:46 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 13:54:46 [INFO] Can continue: There is another way into the temple though, a tunnel<br>from the Underground Pass, built by the dwarves<br>there.
2025-09-12 13:54:46 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:48 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 13:54:48 [INFO] Can continue: Great... Dwarves... I hate dwarves.
2025-09-12 13:54:48 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:49 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:49 [INFO] Can continue: Islwyn
2025-09-12 13:54:49 [INFO] Can continue: You hate everything Ysgawyn.
2025-09-12 13:54:49 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:51 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:51 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:51 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth will stop at nothing to enter the temple.<br>We have to assume that sooner or later, he will find<br>that tunnel.
2025-09-12 13:54:51 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:52 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:52 [INFO] Can continue: Lady Carys Hefin
2025-09-12 13:54:52 [INFO] Can continue: Then we should make sure the tunnel is secure.<br>Baxtorian, allow myself and the other elders to go meet<br>with these dwarves.
2025-09-12 13:54:52 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 13:54:54 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 13:54:54 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 13:54:54 [INFO] Can continue: Very well, head to the Underground Pass and see what<br>you can do. In the meantime, we should secure that<br>orb. Even if he does get into the temple, Lord Iorwerth<br>can do nothing without it.
