2025-09-12 14:08:16 [INFO] Interacting Baxtorian Talk-to
2025-09-12 14:08:18 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:18 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:18 [INFO] Can continue: I've managed to recover the orb.
2025-09-12 14:08:18 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:19 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:19 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:19 [INFO] Can continue: Thank you friend. Without this, Lord Iorwerth has no<br>hope of freeing that fragment of Seren. I will look after<br>it until we decide what to do with it.
2025-09-12 14:08:19 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:20 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:20 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:20 [INFO] Can continue: So what now?
2025-09-12 14:08:20 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:21 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:22 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:22 [INFO] Can continue: We have the orb, and the elders are securing the<br>Temple of Light as we speak. That fragment of Seren<br>should no longer be a concern.
2025-09-12 14:08:22 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:23 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:23 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:23 [INFO] Can continue: But?
2025-09-12 14:08:23 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:24 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:24 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:24 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth is still out there and thanks to his larger<br>army, we have no way of easily dealing with him.
2025-09-12 14:08:24 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:25 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:25 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:25 [INFO] Can continue: There must be something we can do.
2025-09-12 14:08:25 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:26 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:26 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:26 [INFO] Can continue: I'm sure there is, but I don't know what.
2025-09-12 14:08:26 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:27 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:27 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:27 [INFO] Can continue: Perhaps we should call the others then.
2025-09-12 14:08:27 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:29 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:29 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:29 [INFO] Can continue: I was thinking the same. However, I have a favour to<br>ask first. Something I'd rather keep quiet.
2025-09-12 14:08:29 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:30 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:30 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:30 [INFO] Can continue: What is it?
2025-09-12 14:08:30 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:31 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:31 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:31 [INFO] Can continue: Our group is fractured. The revelation about Seren has<br>hit everyone hard, and opinions clearly differ on how we<br>should be responding to it. I fear some intend to take<br>matters into their own hands.
2025-09-12 14:08:31 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:32 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:32 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn in particular has been very distant. I have<br>concerns about his loyalties.
2025-09-12 14:08:32 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:33 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:33 [INFO] Can continue: You don't think he'd join with Lord Iorwerth do you?
2025-09-12 14:08:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:35 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:35 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:35 [INFO] Can continue: I don't know. He claims to hate the Iorwerth clan, and<br>he has more reason to feel that way than most. That<br>said... something isn't right.
2025-09-12 14:08:35 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:36 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:08:36 [INFO] Can continue: And you want me to investigate?
2025-09-12 14:08:36 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:08:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:08:37 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:08:37 [INFO] Can continue: I do. Ysgawyn left the village after the meeting earlier.<br>See if you can track him down and find out what he's<br>up to.
