2025-09-12 14:11:28 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:28 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:28 [INFO] Can continue: Traitor? You dare call me a traitor? Your loyalties<br>change more than the wind and you have the nerve to<br>say I'm the traitor?
