2025-09-12 14:11:29 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:29 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:29 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth took everything from me! My whole life<br>was destroyed by him and that dog, Essyllt! Do you<br>really think I'd join up with them?
