2025-09-12 14:11:29 [INFO] LAG DETECTED 884ms
2025-09-12 14:11:30 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:30 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:11:30 [INFO] Can continue: Well that's what it looks like!
2025-09-12 14:11:30 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:32 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:32 [INFO] Can continue: You fool of a human! I may not agree much with the<br>other rebels but everything I've done has been to stop<br>Lord Iorwerth!
2025-09-12 14:11:32 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:33 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:11:33 [INFO] Can continue: Well who's this then?
2025-09-12 14:11:33 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:34 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:34 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:34 [INFO] Can continue: Well now that you've ruined everything as usual, I<br>suppose I'd better tell you.
