2025-09-12 14:11:35 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:35 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:35 [INFO] Can continue: This is Iestin Edern, head of research for Lord<br>Iorwerth, and my informant within the Iorwerth clan.
2025-09-12 14:11:35 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:36 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:36 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:11:36 [INFO] Can continue: Wait... Your informant?
