2025-09-12 14:11:37 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:37 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:37 [INFO] Can continue: That's right you idiot! Iestin here has been providing<br>me with information on the Iorwerth clan. Not only<br>that, he is the reason why you were able to claim that<br>Orb of Light.
2025-09-12 14:11:37 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:39 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:39 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:11:39 [INFO] Can continue: But... I don't understand. If you've always been loyal,<br>why all the secrecy?
2025-09-12 14:11:39 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:40 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:40 [INFO] Can continue: Iestin
2025-09-12 14:11:40 [INFO] Can continue: That was my request. I feared that the other rebels<br>may not be trusting of me. They could have imprisoned<br>me or even killed me. It seemed safer to keep things<br>secret.
2025-09-12 14:11:40 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:41 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:41 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:11:41 [INFO] Can continue: Not to mention the fact that it kept Iestin safe from<br>any informants that Lord Iorwerth might have among<br>the rebels.
2025-09-12 14:11:41 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:11:42 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:11:42 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:11:42 [INFO] Can continue: I... I see... I guess that all makes sense.
