2025-09-12 14:14:32 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:14:32 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth
2025-09-12 14:14:32 [INFO] Can continue: Well your ability to disappoint is one of your few<br>talents, so I'll let it slide. However, I must insist that<br>you give me the orb.
