2025-09-12 14:14:33 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:14:33 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:14:33 [INFO] Can continue: Crawl back into the hole you came from Lord Iorwerth,<br>you won't leave here with that orb!
