2025-09-12 14:14:47 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:14:47 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth
2025-09-12 14:14:47 [INFO] Can continue: What have I done? Well I told him the truth. It was<br>about time that someone did.
