2025-09-12 14:14:48 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:14:48 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 14:14:48 [INFO] Can continue: They're not the enemy. I thought they were, for so<br>long, but they're not.
