2025-09-12 14:14:50 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:14:50 [INFO] Can continue: Baxtorian
2025-09-12 14:14:50 [INFO] Can continue: You've never sacrificed, you've never lost anything.<br>You only sacrifice those around you...
