2025-09-12 14:14:51 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:14:51 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth
2025-09-12 14:14:51 [INFO] Can continue: You have some nerve to lecture me. Remind me, how<br>many of your people died under your watch? How<br>many fell, trying to free your wife?
