2025-09-12 14:15:02 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:15:02 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth
2025-09-12 14:15:02 [INFO] Can continue: When I first discovered the truth, our clan was still<br>ruled by my mother. I went to her, told her what I'd<br>found, told her what we needed to do.
