2025-09-12 14:15:03 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:15:03 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth
2025-09-12 14:15:03 [INFO] Can continue: I loved my mother, but she was blindly loyal to this fool<br>here, she wouldn't have any of it. I couldn't just<br>abandon my goddess though, she needed us. So I did<br>what had to be done.
2025-09-12 14:15:03 [INFO] Continue
