2025-09-12 14:15:09 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:15:09 [INFO] Can continue: Ysgawyn
2025-09-12 14:15:09 [INFO] Can continue: I'll die before working with them.
2025-09-12 14:15:09 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:15:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:15:10 [INFO] Can continue: Lord Iorwerth
2025-09-12 14:15:10 [INFO] Can continue: No one else needs to die here. Please, just give me the<br>orb. Do that, and I swear we will do you no further<br>harm.
