2025-09-12 14:16:03 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:16:03 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 14:16:03 [INFO] Can continue: For so long I was led to believe that Lord Iorwerth was<br>our enemy. I thought he'd turned his back on Seren,<br>thought he'd betrayed her.
