2025-09-12 14:16:09 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:16:09 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 14:16:09 [INFO] Can continue: My whole life I've dreamed of her, dreamed of what it<br>would be like to meet her. If there's even a chance that<br>she's still alive, I have to know.
2025-09-12 14:16:09 [INFO] Continue
2025-09-12 14:16:10 [INFO] Solving dialogue
2025-09-12 14:16:10 [INFO] Can continue: PLAYER_NAME
2025-09-12 14:16:10 [INFO] Can continue: And if she is alive? Then what?
2025-09-12 14:16:10 [INFO] Continue
