2025-09-12 14:16:12 [INFO] Can continue: Arianwyn
2025-09-12 14:16:12 [INFO] Can continue: Seren guided the elves for thousands of years. With<br>her back, we'll finally be able to reform Prifddinas. We'll<br>finally have peace again.
